#: /home/ynojima/playground/ja.quarkus.io/build/jekyll-source/_versions/2.16/guides/security-keycloak-authorization.adoc
msgid ""
"Any user is allowed to access the\n"
"`http://localhost:8080/api/users/me` endpoint\n"
